@startuml
title market-analysis-engine - Intended Execution Flow

actor User
participant CLI
participant API
participant "FrontendCommandInput" as FCI
participant "build_commands()" as Builder
participant "build_runtime()" as RuntimeBuilder
participant App
participant Handler
participant "TickerService / MarketService / Repo" as Services
participant Event

User -> CLI : run command
User -> API : POST /run

CLI -> FCI : parse CLI args
API -> FCI : parse request body

FCI -> Builder : normalize input
CLI -> RuntimeBuilder : resolve runtime
API -> RuntimeBuilder : resolve/reuse runtime

Builder -> App : executable commands
RuntimeBuilder -> App : runtime dependencies

App -> Handler : resolve handler per command
Handler -> Services : execute business logic
Services --> Handler : data / persistence / fetch results

Handler -> Event : emit log/progress/result/error
Event --> App : stream events
App --> CLI : events
App --> API : events
CLI --> User : render output
API --> User : JSON response
@enduml
